TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local units = Spring.GetTeamUnits(0) for i=1,#units do local unitID = units[i] local unitDefID = Spring.GetUnitDefID(unitID) local x,y,z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID) if unitDefID == UnitDefNames.cormart.id then Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIGHT, {x, y, z - 2000}, {}) else Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.MOVE, {x, y, z - 2000}, {}) end end
units = Spring.GetTeamUnits(1) for i=1,#units do local unitID = units[i] local unitDefID = Spring.GetUnitDefID(unitID) local x,y,z = Spring.GetUnitPosition(unitID) if unitDefID == UnitDefNames.armpw.id then Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.MOVE, {x, y, z + 2000}, {}) end end
